The Mexican Institute of Seguro Social (IMSS) announced that it directs an investigation to discover the gene of the obesity in children and young people, denominated Genetic protocol “of the obesity of the childhood and the adolescence”, that will allow to tell on associated markers the overweight.
In an official notice, the commander of the Unit of Medical Research in Biochemistry of the Hospital of Specialties of the National Medical center 21st century, Miguel Cruz Lopez, explained that a multidisciplinary team of doctors, social nurses was integrated, nutriólogos and workers.
This equipment is supported by specialists and students of postgraduate of the National Institute of Salud Pública (INSP) and of the Advanced Study and Research center (Cinvestav) of the National Polytechnical Institute (IPN).
