Thus it was the work of the Cali that identified the corpse of White Alfonso
A lofoscopista of Cali happened to history like the man who confirmed the death of “White Alfonso”.
The work of these civil servants is key.
The past 4 of November a lofoscopista of the CTI of Cali happened to history like the man who confirmed the identity of the top head of the CRAF: “White Alfonso”, through check off of its fingerprints.
Of the seven lofoscopistas that toil in the sectional one of the CTI, that week touched the turn to him of “availability” to Eliazar González, a Tiled man of Port that has been 21 years working in the area of judicial investigation.
When initiating its race, González worked in municipalities of Chocó, where often it had to go into by more than five days in the forest to arrive at the site in which they were the corpses that had to be identified.
In the 2000 one moved to the capital of the Valley and, after realizing the corresponding courses, specialized in lofoscopia, that is the study of the skin of friction, that is to say, Las Palmas of the hands and the feet.
The week of the operative one against White Alfonso alias to Eliazar they noticed to him that it wore minimum clothes for three days.
Something great hoped to him.
Friday at night left for the Cauca in a helicopter from Palmira.
It knew that it had to identify two corpses and that one suspected that one of them was of the man who directed to the oldest guerilla of the world, reason why they asked to him that he took the card to decadactilar of Guillermo Leon Sáenz (its true name).
Nevertheless, when it arrived with the equipment from investigation at the site in which was the corpse did not recognize it by its physical aspect, because it was very different from which had seen in mass media.
It was without beard, dress like a farmer of the zone, without glasses and much more thin.
But the tracks do not lie.
Accompanied by a galtoniana, red magnifying glass, a transplantador and a lantern, Eliazar it compared the digital impressions of the corpse with those of the card.
Its eye did not fail to him: he was “White Alfonso”.
That same night, the native man of Tiled Port was the one in charge to confirm the minister to him of Defense, Juan Carlos Pinzón, who yes was the top head of the CRAF.
In search of the track
For a dactiloscopista of the Sijín of Cali the recognition that president Juan Manuel Santos to Eliazar González did, in the press conference by operative the con “White”, is very significant.
Much people do not know our work.
The fingerprinting is an exact science, without allowable error, that can get to be key in the resolution of crimes.
Aside from the corpse identification, the lofoscopistas support investigations by crimes as theft and homicide and confirm the identity of the caught people.
When they are captured, many delinquents present false certificates or they do not have papers.
We took the digital impression them and we looked for them in the data base.
The investigator told that, in a case of theft, he was called on to him to clear a piece of wall of a house, because in that place the thief had supported his hand to remove to a box strong full from jewels and money.
“The walls are difficult because they are not appropriate surfaces to remove a digital impression, but in that case we could obtain the track of all the hand and to identify the delinquent, who had participated in different thefts”, remembered.
The tracks can discard or also reaffirm suspects in cases of homicide.
Recently they found a died man, with bottles of liquor to his around.
By means of the investigation it was determined that a relative could be suspicious of the crime and, indeed, a track in the bottle agreed.
Although this does not guarantee that he has been the assassin, yes locates it in the scene of the crime.
A dactiloscopista of the CTI explained that in the objects “the tracks remove with chemical or physical reagents”.
When they appear, a transplantador or tape is used to raise them.
After this, the impressions are sent to the Asif, that is the criminal data base, or to the Registraduría.
“The problem is that still there are many undocumented Colombians”, indicated the expert of the CTI.
It clarified that everything is not as is in the program of CSI television.
As well as everything what shines is not gold, not everything what it is touched becomes track.
Nevertheless, if it can be used, if the respective check off is realized.
